{"tid":39156,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又到聖誕] 施永青提「聖誕」：X你老母","createTime":"2016-12-14T11:41:53.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-14T11:44:44.000Z","uid":34947,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c5b7642cb0ba9792778304083869354fef880f55","tid":39156,"uid":34947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T11:41:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20121218/51189997\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20121218%2F51189997&d=FPxK8sV4H9fbtcXmqkfvBgv3KisNQlPySkJrDkY9tT8%3D&h=86902d53\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20121218%2F51189997&h=ee59f6fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20121218/51189997</a><br />\n<br />\n聖誕前各公司互送聖誕卡、果籃，聊表心意，不過中原地產創辦人施永青對「聖誕」就有Hard Feeling，《壹週刊》報道，施永青一聽到「聖誕」無名火起：「我最憎就是聖誕！」，細個因為屋企窮，無錢買聖誕卡買，所以他將人哋送畀佢張聖誕卡，改咗自己個名送畀人，點知同學將件事唱通街，超慘！仲話，「我已經同佢反左面架喇！」<br />\n<br />\n依家施永青財力雄厚，想送幾多果籃塞住人哋把口都得啦！佢話雖然收大把果籃，但一個都唔會送出去，仲好激動咁話，「你咪唔好同我做生意囉，笨！我X你老母」嚇到個記者打咗個突，童年的影響之大，真係唔講得笑！"},{"pid":"30fbcbd3344440d5b4964659030c1ade58cad86c","tid":39156,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T11:43:10.000Z","msg":"睇親都笑, 明明自己做錯"},{"pid":"7204e49f0fe76e5d10306ab23004a878c6393075","tid":39156,"uid":6677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T11:44:44.000Z","msg":"每次見到呢個title就知道，嗯，聖誕就到了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}